# Data manipulation

Using a data file with the following content in a format that doesn't follow a standard.

```data
IntegerValue = 1
FloatValue = 1.23
StringValue = "Foo bar"
EquationResult = {{ add 2 (power (mul 2 3) 6) }}
ListValue = ["value1", "value2"]
DictValue = {"key1": "value1", "key2": "value2"}
```

## toYaml

| Razor | Gotemplate
| ---   | ---
| ```{{ toYaml (data "!Data") }}``` | ```{{ toYaml (data "!Data") }}```

```data
DictValue:
  key1: value1
  key2: value2
EquationResult: 46658
FloatValue: 1.23
IntegerValue: 1
ListValue:
- value1
- value2
StringValue: Foo bar
```

